{"tid":1366624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【FF 】光復元朗worst-case 『沙盤推演』","createTime":"2019-07-26T04:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T04:12:34.000Z","uid":269761,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ff8d96764783390159bb6e394b415794c40141","tid":1366624,"uid":269761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復元朗worst-case 沙盤推演<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88bmyJT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88bmyJT.png&h=22732b59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">反對通知書已發出，政府不再形式上保護巿民，元朗當天一定變死城，雖然<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">街上被圍毆機會不大</span></strong>，但「照去」的朋友請考慮以下可能性：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暴力 1 偷襲</span></span>，從樓上飛嘢落街、暗器傷人，完全無仇報，而警察...  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暴力 2 綁架</span></span>，落單嘅被打完拉入村，溶咗你都得，而警察...  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暴力 3 恐襲</span></span>，個別人仕孤狼式開車撞人，攞刀劈人，大傷亡造成恐慌，而警察...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上三項都會引致嚴重受傷，而<span style=\"color: purple;\">非法活動保險肯定唔包。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我估計警方明天未出發前會<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拘捕發起人</span></span>，扣留48小時，當然只係無咗一個人物，其他人會照行。但要注意：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟據6.12 Telegram 受國家級攻擊經歷，明天極有可能<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">通訊受阻</span></span>，無大台嘅弱點，請自行研究對策。緊記，事前<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">擬定逃生方式，當你無得睇地圖同搵車/call 車，係好很麻煩。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警方已經whe 難塊面，都唔怕再開槍，水炮車、圍城、清場、拉人。頭先講過，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>死咗都無保險</strong></span>，若被捕，好大可能就證明你參與非法集結/暴動。所以，<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>form 小組行街，「夾定」幾點做咩邊度等，唔好帶標語，幾多人去，幾多人走。裝備啲咩係兩難，多就怕被人入，少又怕被人揼，自己衡量。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得做義仕，死都預咗，但如果<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重傷係一世</span></span></strong>嘅，DGS 老師被打中眼係例子，永久受損，如果無保險其實都幾慘。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以往「公民抗命」考量已經唔work，對方用接近無底線嘅攻擊，「代價」變成無可估計，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Be water, my friend。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGod bless Hong Kong.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}